In desktop era, where computer applications are meant to be personal, there is
not much of a need for notifications. In the internet era, where application
like Zeta acts as a central point interfacing with multiple users, co-ordinating
their information, it is imperative that other users need to be notified on
informations that matters to them.

We have build quite a few notification methods for our users. Like, favorites
where users can get changes that are done to their project, wiki, ticket etc.
via email, syndication feeds in atleast a dozen variations consumed using
your preferred RSS reader, user invitations, resetting forgotten passwords, and
more ...
